#ROOM
Vnum     43200
Name     &WThe Entryway of Ahn'Qiraj&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The blinding white sands of Silithus are replaced by the cool, 
stagnant air of the inner temple. Massive white sandstone 
pillars reach toward the dark ceiling, and the walls are etched 
with the history of the Qiraji empire. A long, descending ramp 
leads deep into the earth.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    39100
Desc      Return to the Scarab Wall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43201
Desc      The path into the deep.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43201
Name     &WThe Hall of the Swarm&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide thoroughfare carved from solid stone. The walls are 
lined with hundreds of small alcoves where silithid swarm-guards 
stand in silent vigil. The air hums with a permanent, 
low-frequency buzzing.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43200
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43202
Desc      The Chamber of the Prophet.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43012 10 43201
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43202
Name     &WThe Chamber of the Prophet&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber. In the center, a raised stone 
platform is used by the Prophet Skeram to preach to the 
assembled legions. The air here tastes of ozone and madness. 
Three images of the Prophet flicker on the dais.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43201
Desc      The entry hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43210
Desc      Toward the Bug Trio.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43000 1 43202
  Reset G 1 43100 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43210
Name     &WThe Road to the Swarm - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stone halls are replaced by a more organic, hive-like 
environment. The walls are made of a hardened resin, and 
the ceiling is covered in thick webs. The Bug Trio—Vem, 
Yauj, and Kri—patrol this intersection.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43202
Desc      Skeram's chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43220
Desc      Toward huhuran's garden.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43009 1 43210
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43220
Name     &WThe Garden of huhuran - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A beautiful but dangerous garden of subterranean flowers and 
ferns. The air is thick with a toxic green pollen, and 
the sound of beating wings is constant. Princess 
Huhuran circles the high rafters.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43210
Desc      The swarm road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43230
Desc      Toward the Twin Emperors.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43001 1 43220
  Reset G 1 43109 1
Reset M 0 43031 10 43220
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43230
Name     &WThe Hall of Emperors - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The architecture here is grand and clínica, with white marble 
pillars carved in the image of massive winged sentinels. 
The air is clear of smoke, but the sense of dread 
only increases. High-ranking dragonspawn stand in 
silent vigil.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43220
Desc      Huhuran's garden.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43231
Desc      The Throne of the Twins.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43017 5 43230
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43231
Name     &WThe Throne of the Twin Emperors&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The highest point of the upper temple. Emperor Vek'nilash 
and Emperor Vek'lor sit upon dual thrones, their eyes 
glowing with unholy power. They oversee the final 
corruption of Kalimdor from this very seat. The 
air hums with the power of the Old Gods.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43230
Desc      The hall entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    43240
Desc      The Descent to C'Thun.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43002 1 43231
Reset M 0 43003 1 43231
  Reset G 1 43111 1
Reset M 0 43022 10 43231
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43240
Name     &WThe Descent to C'Thun - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A steep set of stairs leads down into the heart of the 
mountain. The walls are damp and the air reeks of 
Hopelessness and old rot. The sound of a giant 
heartbeat thrums through the floor.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    43231
Desc      The twins' throne.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43250
Desc      The Chamber of C'Thun.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43013 10 43240
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43250
Name     &rThe Chamber of C'Thun&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You have reached the absolute heart of madness. A massive, 
circular pool of darkness nearly five hundred feet wide sits 
in the center of the room. In the middle of the pit, the 
monstrous Eye of C'Thun stares at you, unblinking. The 
very air screams with the whispers of the Old God.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43240
Desc      The descent entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    43401
Desc      The exit path.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43005 1 43250
  Reset G 1 43117 1
  Reset E 1 43101 1 16
Reset M 0 43041 20 43250
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43251
Name     &WThe Hall of Sartura&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide circular room near the entrance. Battleguard 
Sartura stands here, surrounded by her personal 
guard. She is a whirlwind of blades and fury.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    43201
Desc      Hall of Swarm.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43006 1 43251
  Reset G 1 43110 1
Reset M 0 43006 5 43251
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43252
Name     &WThe Lair of Fankriss&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive circular chamber filled with hundreds of small 
sand-reaver hatchlings. Fankriss the Unyielding stands 
in the center, his golden armor reflecting the dim light.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    43210
Desc      Swarm road.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43007 1 43252
Reset M 0 43026 20 43252
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43253
Name     &WThe Lair of Ouro&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone platform overlooking a massive pool of 
white sand. Ouro often rises from the center of 
the pit, his body shaking the foundations of 
the temple.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    43240
Desc      Descent entry.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43004 1 43253
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     43254
