Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A deep, circular pit filled with freezing green slime. 
Viscidus stands in the center, his body pulsing with 
necrotic energy.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    43210
Desc      Swarm road.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 43008 1 43254
#ENDROOM

